==External links== * [http://www.helsinki.fi/science/commens/dictionary.html ''The Commens Dictionary of Peirce's Terms''] edited by Mats Bergman and Sami Paavola * [http://www.gnusystems.ca/PeircePhenom.htm Charles S. Peirce's Phaneroscopy and Phenomenology] by Gary Fuhrman
